text: is a art museum of a prefecture in eastern Kyushu. It is in the city of Miyazaki. The museum has artworks by artists who are either from Miyazaki Prefecture or who are in some way connected to it.Miyasaki Prefectural Art Museum, Our Collection; retrieved 2012-2-9. ==History== The museum was first opened in 1995.Miyasaki Prefectural Art Museum, Home; retrieved 2012-2-9. ==References== ==Other websites== * Miyazaki Prefectural Art Museum website ; Category:Art museums in Japan Category:Buildings and structures in Miyazaki Prefecture
title: Miyazaki Prefectural Art Museum
